      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-09-04T12:59:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Right, but could you make a GrRenderTargetContext with the backend format + color type if this flag was not set? That seems like a useful thing to be able to do internally (e.g. to issue a draw for some read/write pixels conversion) that is separable from whether we want to allow SkSurfaces with a color type.",
